*mbrola-3.0.1h-r4 (02 Apr 2006)

  02 Apr 2006; William Hubbs <williamh@gentoo.org> +mbrola-3.0.1h-r4.ebuild:
  Added Italian and Romanian language support.
  Closes #123251 and #125355.

  03 Mar 2006; Simon Stelling <blubb@gentoo.org> mbrola-3.0.1h-r1.ebuild,
  mbrola-3.0.1h-r3.ebuild:
  remove the dependency on app-emulation/emul-linux-x86-glibc since 2004.3 has
  been deprecated a while ago

  16 Feb 2006; Diego Petten√≤ <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  mbrola-3.0.1h-r1.ebuild, mbrola-3.0.1h-r3.ebuild:
  Make unzip a build-time depenndency.

  24 Aug 2005; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> mbrola-3.0.1h-r3.ebuild:
  add ~alpha ~ia64

  28 Jul 2005; Guy Martin <gmsoft@gentoo.org> mbrola-3.0.1h-r3.ebuild:
  Added ~hppa to KEYWORDS.

*mbrola-3.0.1h-r3 (25 Jul 2005)

